<h2>Governor committees and working groups</h2>

<p class="lead">As well as quarterly Council meetings, our governors also attend smaller committees and working groups that conduct detailed reviews of topical issues.</p>

<div class="cols cols--two">
<div class="col col--one">
<h3>Patient Experience and safety</h3>

<p class="secondary">Listens to patients to understand how we can improve the experience of patients at King’s and ensure their safety.</p>
</div><!-- col -->

<div class="col col--two">
<h3>Strategy</h3>

<p class="secondary">Reviews plans and strategies for the future of the hospital, representing the views of members and the needs of the local community.</p>
</div><!-- col -->

</div><!-- cols -->

<h3>Membership and community engagement</h3>

<p>Aims to grow and develop the Trust’s membership and facilitates communication between governors, Members and the local community.</p>

